name: Dr. Shahin Jessa
about:
Dr. Jessa, born and raised in Kenya, settled in Vancouver with her family as a teenager. She earned her Bachelor of Science degree in Human Nutrition from the University of British Columbia. She then completed her Doctorate of Dental Medicine degree at UBC in 1996.
